Package: clusterconf
Title: Interface with clusterconf.cluster packages to read cluster configurations
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matt", "Pollock", email = "mpollock@mitre.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Brendan", "Hogan", email = "bhogan@mitre.org", role = "aut", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4010-5224")),
    person(family = "The MITRE Corporation", email = "opensource@mitre.org", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: The clusterconf.* package parent. This package will handle reading in configurations,
  parsing out parameter values from configurations, and tracking/installing cluster-specific 
  configuration packages.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
Imports: config
